<div><head>會稽記</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a.2">《軼雲蔽日》</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a.3">四明山高峰軼雲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a.4">連岫蔽日。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a.5">《秦望》</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a.6">會稽秦望山為眾峰之傑，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a.7">陟境便見。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a.8">《史記》云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a.9">秦始皇登之以望南海。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a.10">自平地以取山頂七里，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a.11">縣嶝孤危，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a.12">峭路險絕。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a.13">《記》云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a.14">扳蘿捫葛然後能升，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a.15">山上無高木，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a.16">當由地逈多風所致。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a.17">山南有嶕峴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a.18">峴裏有大城，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-1a.19">越不無餘之舊都也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-2a.2">《映發》</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-2a.3">會稽境特多名山水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-2a.4">峰崿隆峻，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-2a.5">吐納雲霧，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-2a.6">松栝楓柏，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-2a.7">摧榦竦條，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-2a.8">澄壑鏡徹，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-2a.9">清流寫注。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-3a.2">《白樓》</seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-3a.3">江夏太守宋輔於重山南白樓亭立學教授，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-3a.4">沛國桓儼避地至會稽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-3a.5">聞陳業賢而往候之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-3a.6">不見，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-3a.7">臨去入交州，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-3a.8">留書繫白樓亭柱而別。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-3a.9">孫興公、許玄度共在白樓亭共商略先往名達，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-3a.10">林公既非所關，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-3a.11">聽訖云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-3a.12">二賢故自有才情。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-3a.13">亭在山陰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1728_CHANT_001-3a.14">臨流映壑也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
